try is exclusively for registered UIC Students  – The pantry serves for emergency life circumstances or financial difficulties  – Please register at Wellness Center’s front desk during non-pantry hours.*Hours are subject to change for summer session*       2020 Spring Semester Events   2020 Events  *ALL events for Spring 2020 are canceled due to COVID-19 and University policies.      January       Program  Date  Location  Time Frame      Blood Pressure Screenings  Wednesday, 1/29  Wellness Center  10 AM- 1 PM                             February       Program  Date  Location  Time Frame      Let's Talk About Love Workshop  Monday, 2/10  SCE 610  2 PM- 3 PM    DIY Paint Your Own Pencil Pouch  Wednesday, 2/12  WC  11 AM-1 PM    Staying Safe In the City  Monday, 2/17  CSRC, Quiet Room  2 PM- 3 PM         March       Program  Date  Location  Time Frame      Pop-Up Photo-booth
